Usage: NET server [port] [nickname] [username] [realname]
  Connects to server in another window

  Creates a new window and connects it to specified server.
  Default port is 6667.
  ^W? Shows you this help screen.
  ^WK Kills the current window.
  ^WH Hides the current window.
  ^WC Clears the current window.
  ^WL Lists all windows.
  ^WP Goes to the previous window.
  ^WN Goes to the next window. 
  ^WR Reduces window 1 line.
  ^WG Grows window 1 line.
  ^W<1-9> Changes to window number <1-9>.
